				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Personally I dont see the point in cheating in online games.  Sure, you have a feeling of empowerment but it just ruins the game for you and your opponents.  I used to be into finding all the latest hacks for stuff and getting any extra edge I could but I found I got bored of those games really fast.  After I burned through a couple games like that I figured it just wasn't sustainable and in the long run I would have less fun.
<br />

<br />
What do you all think?
<br />

